dc_description_s: State lands for sale in 1925 indicated in red.; In each township with a red dot, the state is offering, at public auction, various tracts of state-owned land.; On verso: Index and text itemizing the terms of sale.; Insets: Mesabi Range -- Cook County -- St. Paul-Minneapolis and vicinity.|71 x 50 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:925,000|General Minnesota Maps
